      "width": 500,
      "height": 280,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# VS Code Landing Surface\n\nCreate a VS Code-first entry surface that drops the user into a workspace with:\n\n- agent on one side\n- files on one side\n- graph in the middle\n\nThis is not just a marketing page. It is a concrete workstation story.",
